<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="glass-panel rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">What is the SUS Token?</h3>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-accent-blue">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-white/10">
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">SUS is a utility token that tokenizes agricultural land and carbon credits, allowing you to participate in sustainable farming in Africa.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-panel rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">How does the Impact Simulation work?</h3>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-accent-blue">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="p-6 pt-0 border-t border-white/10">
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">It uses real-world data from our moringa farms to estimate your potential environmental impact and financial returns based on the number of SUS tokens you hold.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="glass-panel rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group">
<summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">How can I join the waitlist?</h3>
